# Triage labels

Skills such as **triage** use five roles; map them to these **exact** GitHub label names:

| Role | Label |
|------|-------|
| Maintainer must evaluate | `needs-triage` |
| Waiting on reporter | `needs-info` |
| Fully specified, AFK-agent ready | `ready-for-agent` |
| Needs human implementation | `ready-for-human` |
| Will not be actioned | `wontfix` |

Details: `docs/agents/triage-labels.md`.
